WEBVTT

00:00.232 --> 00:01.530
Previously, on The OC:

00:01.546 --> 00:03.745
What, are you saying you want to be social chair?

00:03.802 --> 00:04.694
Maybe.

00:04.797 --> 00:05.509
Don't move.

00:05.575 --> 00:06.503
I didn't steal anything.

00:06.564 --> 00:07.751
One month detention.

00:07.812 --> 00:09.603
Unless you want to give up your partner...

00:09.667 --> 00:11.598
They're reading Caleb's will on Friday.

00:11.654 --> 00:15.218
From what you told me about your dad, I'd bet he's planned a surprise for you.

00:15.275 --> 00:16.578
Caleb Nichol was broke.

00:16.799 --> 00:17.306
Broke?

00:17.367 --> 00:19.856
Ryan and I don't go to Harbor, but it'll be fine.

00:19.912 --> 00:21.110
At least you guys have each other.

00:21.166 --> 00:23.398
If you stick together, everything will be okay.

00:23.954 --> 00:24.751
- Deal?
- Deal.

